#: ../../source/unit/digi_clock.rst:2 42e26fd7bc45433fb0a143e2af4e03be
msgid "DigiClock Unit"
msgstr "DigiClock Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/digi_clock.rst:6 e9bae1cdb96d45a39ebe34e2d10a8c32
msgid ""
"UNIT-Digi-Clock is a 2.1 inch 4-digit 7-segment display module. There are"
" decimal points on each digit and an extra wire for colon-dots in the "
"center, which can display Decimals and Clock. This module adopts TM1637 "
"as the driver IC, and STM32F030 as I2C communication. I2C address can be "
"modified per 4-bit dip switch. The red LED supports 8 brightness. And we "
"have reserved 4 fixing holes there."
msgstr ""
"UNIT-Digi-Clock 是一款 2.1 英寸 4 "
"位数码管（7-segment）显示模块。每一位数字都带有小数点，并额外提供一根用于中间冒号点的连线，可用于显示小数与时钟。该模块采用 TM1637"
" 作为驱动 IC，并使用 STM32F030 进行 I2C 通信。I2C 地址可通过 4-bit 拨码开关修改。红色 LED 支持 8 "
"档亮度，并预留了 4 个固定孔位。"

